high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the fridge, turn left, go forward and then left to the oven, face the oven.
Take the pot on the right of the stove top.
Turn right, go forward to the sink.
Fill the pot with water in the sink. Take the pot from the sink.
Turn around, go back to the stove top.
Put the pot on the right back burner of the stove top.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot filled with water on a stove top.

high_descs: Turn around and veer right around kitchen island, then left to the stove.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the pot in the sink.
Turn around and walk back to the stove.
Place the clean pot on the back right burner.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pot on a stove top.

high_descs: Pick up a pot from the stove
Put the pot in the sink and fill it with water
Put the pot on the stove
